item.enchancement_unbound.orbital_strike: A strange device from a lost world, floatin' in the cosmos. It seems to use the firepower that there comes from this here world. The text on the screen reads in the standard galactic alphabet, although its meanin' be unclearrr. Somethin' about travelin' through wormholes?
item.enchancement_unbound.amethyst_shard: This item noms purpur shinee for breakfast.
item.enchancement_unbound.ice_shard_mini: This item noms pack'd Frozen Water and big blu for breakfast.
death.attack.enchancement_unbound.midas_: %1$s decided to play with powers they did not deserve
death.attack.enchancement_unbound.forced: %1$s forcibly gathered knowledge from another an' paid the price
item.enchancement_unbound.slingshot.intr: This ancient weapon used to 'ave a name, but it been lost to the sands o' time. Ye found it, restin' nearrr a tree that there enamated unusual energy. It looks like it may 'ave come from another dimension,
item.enchancement_unbound.slingshot.ayly: one o' otherwordly creatures an' towerin' forests...
enchantment.enchancement_unbound.curtain: Puts entities into a "curtain" state, where they take more damage dependin' on 'ow many times they 'ave been hit by this magic. Effect ends after one minute a while o' no hits, after which the entity will become immune to bein' "curtained" fer a few seconds.
enchantment.enchancement_unbound.ascensi: Usin' the shovel on the bottom o' a block will make the user ascend until they reach non-solid blocks.
enchantment.enchancement_unbound.executi: About 2.5% chance to instantly execute the entity. Entities that there cannot be executed, such as bosses an' players, will take increased damage instead. Only activates when the target 'as 40% health or lower, but chance o' activatin' increases with how wounded the target be, to a maximum o' 5% at around 0.2% health remainin'.
enchantment.enchancement_unbound.midas_t: Turns entities into gold upon hit. The effect will reverse when the entity touches water or rain. Does not work in ultrawarm dimensions such as the Nether. Can only be applied on gold tools.
enchantment.enchancement_unbound.apple_s: Breakin' leaves has a change o' dropping extra scurvy's cures. Also has a chance o' getting witchcraft'd golden apples. Greatly increases the hoe's minin' speed when breakin' leaves.
enchantment.enchancement_unbound.soul_re: Adds knowledge to the attacker an' drains the target o' knowledge if it has any. Forcibly gatherin' knowledge from another livin' bein' can't have any negative consequences, right?
enchantment.enchancement_unbound.sentien: On being damaged, the greaves will run off and attack entities. Right-click the greaves entity to get the greaves (item) back.
